javascript is a hight level object oriented, multi paradigm
programming language.

high level language-: we don't need to worry about complex stuff like memory management.
programming language-: instruct computer to do things.
object-oriented-: based on objects, for storing most kinds of data.
multi paradigm-: we can use different style of programming.

role of javascript in web development

programming language: building web applications.


for dynamic and web application in the browser(front end apps)

react, angular


web applications on web servers(back end apps)

node js


native mobile applications 

react, ionic


native desktop applications

electron.